{"address1": "Lakshmi Narayan Complex", "address2": "5th Floor 10/1, Palace Road", "city": "Bengaluru", "zip": "560052", "country": "India", "phone": "91 80 4137 9500", "fax": "91 80 2235 4057", "website": "https://www.balpharma.com", "industry": "Drug Manufacturers - Specialty & Generic", "industryKey": "drug-manufacturers-specialty-generic", "industryDisp": "Drug Manufacturers - Specialty & Generic", "sector": "Healthcare", "sectorKey": "healthcare", "sectorDisp": "Healthcare", "longBusinessSummary": "Bal Pharma Limited, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and markets pharmaceutical formulations and active pharmaceutical ingredients (APIs) in India and internationally. The company offers prescription drugs, generics, OTC products, intravenous infusion products, and bulk drugs. It also provides anti-infectives, pain management, respiratory care, and women's health products under the Aziwin, Ebay, Balvibe, MNF, Ocium, and Monogesic Plus Gel brands; diabetic care products under the Diabend and Diabend M Group brands; herbal/ayurvedic preparations targeting conditions, such as prostate enlargement, renal calculi, male infertility, and women health, etc. under the Stonex, Ashwamed, Prostowin, Suswas, Menoleap, and Ayursulin brands; anti-hypertensive, anti-lipidemic, and anti-obese products; skin care and bone health products; herbal liver protective and antioxidant; and cardiac care products under the Secremet and Servace brands. In addition, the company offers a range of APIs for therapeutic areas, such as anti-histamine, platelet inhibitor, anti-diabetic, anti-convulsant, urinary incontinence, neuropathic pain, anti-allergy, anti-inflammatory, diuretic, and acne treatment, etc.; and various formulations, including tablets, capsules, syrups, suspensions, ophthalmic, creams, and ointments. Further, it engages in the treatment of gastrointestinal disorders; and piles, fistula, and constipation. The company exports its products to approximately 30 countries. Bal Pharma Limited was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Bengaluru, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 986, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Shailesh Dheerajmal Siroya", "age": 59, "title": "MD & Executive Director", "yearBorn": 1966, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 18333000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Daddanala Venkat Bharath Bhushan", "age": 36, "title": "Chief Financial Officer", "yearBorn": 1989, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Archana Dubey Mitra", "age": 51, "title": "Chief Operating Officer", "yearBorn": 1974, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Abdul  Basith", "title": "Company Secretary & Compliance Officer", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Himesh  Virupakshaya", "age": 64, "title": "Whole Time Director", "yearBorn": 1961, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 3713000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Ravindra Kumar Kothari", "age": 70, "title": "Deputy GM of Internal Audit, Legal and Compliances & Non-Executive and Non-Independent Director", "yearBorn": 1955, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. D. L. Bhat", "age": 62, "title": "Assistant Vice President of Sales & Marketing", "yearBorn": 1963, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "N Subrahmanyeswara Rao", "age": 53, "title": "Senior General Manager", "yearBorn": 1972, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ezaz Kaseem Azmi", "age": 43, "title": "General Manager", "yearBorn": 1982, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Bidyut Kumar Bhattacharrya", "age": 49, "title": "General Manager of Purchase", "yearBorn": 1976, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValu